            <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in v1.1 (12)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Fixed 4-shot FFF black export</b> — eager render breaks lazy CIRAWFilter chain on Intel</li>
                    <li><b>Color profile fix</b> — uses CIRAWFilter output color space for Hasselblad FFF</li>
                    <li><b>Auto-crop in Minimal Crop</b> — automatically maximizes content (wall/background)</li>
                    <li><b>Export via CGImageDestination</b> — explicit 16-bit TIFF with ICC profile</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
